# Intent Spec 收紧报告 — cli-ux-command-tree-redesign

> intent-spec-writer 把 PRD / PDR-001 的 intent seed 收紧为 cli-ux 产品内可检查的正式 intent-lang。

## Summary

| 指标 | 值 |
|---|---|
| 目标产品 | `cli-ux` |
| 来源种子 | `products/cli-ux/intents/acceptance.intent` |
| 正式化 intent 数 | 7 |
| 剥离约束数（降级到 task）| 0 |
| `intent check` exit | 0 |
| 结论 | 可合并 |

一句话结论：cli-ux 迁移采用新设计契约，formal intent 覆盖 init、issue/run、doc artifact、stage advance、actionable error、admin boundary 与 command disposition，不要求 legacy stdout byte parity。

## Ingest Checklist

- [x] 种子已读，列出其全部 intent / type
- [x] 目标产品现有三件套已读，已列出现存符号名（去重基线）
- [x] PRD § Intent Mapping 已读，每条声明目标层已确认
- [x] 每条种子内容已初步标好归属层

## 分层归位

| 来源（PRD Intent Mapping）| 归属层 | 落点文件 | 形态 | 备注 |
|---|---|---|---|---|
| InitShowsNextStep | acceptance | `products/cli-ux/intents/acceptance.intent` | intent require/ensure | trivial verified |
| IssueStartCreatesRun | acceptance | `products/cli-ux/intents/acceptance.intent` | intent require/ensure | trivial verified |
| DocCommandWritesArtifact | acceptance | `products/cli-ux/intents/acceptance.intent` | intent require/ensure | trivial verified |
| StageAdvanceReflectsState | acceptance | `products/cli-ux/intents/acceptance.intent` | intent require/ensure | trivial verified |
| ErrorsAreActionable | acceptance | `products/cli-ux/intents/acceptance.intent` | intent require/ensure | trivial verified |
| AdminCommandsAreExplicit | acceptance | `products/cli-ux/intents/acceptance.intent` | intent require/ensure | trivial verified |
| RemovedCommandsStayRemoved / RenderTopLevelHelp | invariants | `products/cli-ux/intents/invariants.intent` | safety + binding intent | true VC verified |
| CLI shell delegates domain behavior | contracts | `products/cli-ux/intents/contracts.intent` | goal rationale/stakeholder/measure | ADR-007 Accepted，0 VC |

## 剥离的约束

（无）

本 slice 明确不把 legacy stdout byte parity、耗时、性能和运行时实现细节写入 `.intent`；delivery 阶段用语义 golden、CLI tests 与 cutover ADR 守护。

## 四规则审查

- [x] 规则 1：所有后态约束使用 primed `x'`
- [x] 规则 2：acceptance 文件只放操作规约，保持型不变量独立放入 invariants
- [x] 规则 3：本批没有要求 frame 的未改字段；如 delivery 增加状态字段，需显式补 `ensure x' == x`
- [x] 规则 4：acceptance 的 require/ensure 是 trivial verified；command-surface 不变量在 invariants 中产生真实 VC

